folder.name: Non Validated Components
folder.memo:
NB. The models in this folder have not been through the APSIM validation process.
These models are not supported, have not been reviewed by the APSIM Reference Panel and have not been validated through the rigorous process required for APSIM 'official' models.
They may be incomplete, non functional, or worse. They are intended for the use of the developer community.

script.text:
SimDay = 1
AccumPlantN = 0 AccumMineralisation = 0 AccumDenit = 0 AccumFert = 0 AccumLeach = 0 AccumDetach = 0 DeltaSoilOMN = 0 DeltaSurfaceOMN = 0 DeltaSoilMineralN = 0
AccumEO = 0 AccumEP = 0 AccumES = 0 AccumDrainage = 0 AccumRunoff = 0 AccumIrrigation = 0 AccumRainfall = 0 SoilWaterDeficit = 0

if simday = 1 then InitialSoilOMN = biom_n() + fom_n() + hum_n() InitialSurfaceOMN = surfaceom_n InitialMineralN = no3() + nh4() + urea() endif
!!!!!! Nitrogen balance components !!!!!! !!!!!!^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^!!!!!! AccumPlantN = (0 - [CropType].leafliveN2 - [CropType].leafdeadn2 - [CropType].stemliven - [CropType].stemdeadn - [CropType].tuberliveN - [CropType].tuberdeadN ) * 10 ![CropType].RootLiveN + [CropType].RootDeadN AccumMineralisation = AccumMineralisation + dlt_n_min() + dlt_n_min_res() AccumDenit = AccumDenit - dnit() AccumFert = AccumFert + fertiliser AccumLeach = AccumLeach - leach_urea - leach_no3 - leach_nh4 AccumDetach = 0 !plant2 doesn't detach yet DeltaSoilOMN = (biom_n() + fom_n() + hum_n()) - InitialSoilOMN DeltaSurfaceOMN = surfaceom_n - InitialSurfaceOMN DeltaSoilMineralN = (no3() + nh4() + urea()) - InitialMineralN
!!!!!! Water balance components !!!!!! !!!!!!^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^!!!!!!
AccumEO = AccumEO - eo AccumEP = AccumEP - [CropType].LeafTranspiration AccumES = AccumES - es AccumDrainage = AccumDrainage - drain AccumRunoff = AccumRunoff - runoff AccumOutflowLat = AccumOutflowLat - outflow_lat() AccumIrrigation = AccumIrrigation + Irrigation AccumRainfall = Accumrainfall + rain SoilWaterDeficit = sw_dep() - dul_dep()
if SimDay = 1 then SimDay = 2 Else SimDay = 2 endif
